## Error in Original Calculations {#sec-calculation-error}

There is one discrepancy between this table and [GiveWell's spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1WqNL0PEA4cT470ALp0nItEEU8gM_IlhVNIJK1GqnFVE/edit?gid=1419867728#gid=1419867728) cells `F7`, `F8`, and `F14`.  This is because the original spreadsheet has the incorrect forumla in `F7`. The formula it ought to have in `F7` is `=C34`.  The correct value in cell `F7` is `90.4%`.  This incorrect value then affects the totals in `F8` and `F14`.

